Poptip,is,a,service,for,quickly,collecting,peoples,opinions,via,Twitter,Journalists,brands,and,curious,individuals,can,use,the,service,to,tweet,a,question,and,collect,their,followers,responses,Followers,reply,to,queries,directly,through,Twitter,and,Poptip,aggregates,and,displays,the,responses,in,real,time,The,Poptip,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,Poptip,s,crowd,participation,functions,into,their,applications